From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Sun, 16 Nov 2025 22:39:58 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 10/12] Add pan/zoom controls and fix instant rendering for
 Excalidraw maps

Features:
- Pan: Drag with mouse or touch to move around the map
- Zoom: Mouse wheel or +/- buttons to zoom in/out
- Reset button to restore original view
- Support for touch devices
- Instant rendering on SPA navigation using "nav" event

UI Improvements:
- Control buttons positioned at bottom-right
- Smooth transitions and hover effects
- Grab cursor during panning
- Zoom limits (0.1x - 10x)

Documentation:
- Added QUARTZ_INTEGRATION.md with implementation details
- Documented data format and compression method
- Listed supported element types and limitations

Cleanup:
- Removed test-map.excalidraw.md (corrupted data)
- Removed debug logging from transformer
